# NOAA BlueTopo national bathymetry, US navigable waters. Run from pipelines/:  just ../sources/bluetopo/
# Streaming model: resolve the tile-scheme GeoPackage, register every populated tile
# as a /vsicurl/ reference (header reads only — no download). Aggregation range-reads
# the COGs from S3. Per-tile UTM zones + 3-band rasters: metadata sets mixed_crs + band
# so the reproject warps heterogeneous CRS and selects the elevation band. No
# normalize/datum/tarball (tiles are already COGs; MLLW->MSL deferred to Phase 5).
[no-cd]
default:
    uv run python source_register_remote_geopkg.py bluetopo
